1.3.1 hclust

#22
par(mfrow = c(2,2))

#
method <- c("complete","single","average","ward.D")

#
library(dendextend)
for (i in 1:4) {
  metro16 %>% 
    select(2:6) %>% 
    scale() %>% 
    dist() %>% 
    hclust(method = method[i]) %>% 
    as.dendrogram() %>% 
    color_branches(k = 3) %>% 
    plot(main = method[i])  
}

#
metro16.ward <- metro16 %>% 
    select(2:6) %>% 
    scale() %>% 
    dist() %>% 
    hclust(method = method[i])

Ward.D367

library(cluster)

metro16 %>% select(2:6) %>%

    fviz_dend(k = 3,  #
          cex = 0.6,  # 
          k_colors = c(4,5,6), #
          color_labels_by_k = TRUE, #
          rect = TRUE,  #
          lower_rect = -2, 
          main = "Linkage Method: Ward")  #

metro16.agnes <- metro16 %>% select(2:6) %>% 
    agnes(stand = TRUE, method = "ward")
